Do you recognize this as yourself, Mr. Epstein, and again, Frances Jardine? A. I do. Q. Okay. And I'm assuming, again -- and this is in 1994 -- that you don't have a specific memory of this flight; is that right? A. I do not remember this flight. Q. Okay. MR.
